凡人不管不顾！"]},{"code":231,"indent":0,"parameters":[2,"15-LH2",0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2,"墨轩"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["在本座看来你只是在逃避自己糟糕的过去而已，既然你选择了修仙，选择了复仇，那还犹豫什么，至于百姓？区区百姓而已，他们只会记得谁对他们好，现在百姓不都在说新帝的好吗"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2,"墨轩"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["还有，小丫头，下次再打断我说话，我会让你直接从这个世界消失。"]},{"code":231,"indent":0,"parameters":[2,"3-LH",0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2,"阿欢"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["... ..."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2,"\\n[1]"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\Face[2]你说的对。"]},{"code":231,"indent":0,"parameters":[2,"3-LH",0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2,"阿欢"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["公主... ..."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2,"\\n[1]"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\Face[3]阿欢，我想一个人走走，你在家里等我，我会...回来的... ..."]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[22]},{"code":211,"indent":0,"parameters":[0]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[115]},{"code":231,"indent":0,"parameters":[1,"HS",0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,1,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["当天晚上... ..."]},{"code":201,"indent":0,"parameters":[0,58,0,8,6,0]},{"code":0,"indent":0,"parameters":[]}],"moveFrequency":3,"moveRoute":{"list":[{"code":0,"parameters":[]}],"repeat":true,"skippable":false,"wait":false},"moveSpeed":3,"moveType":0,"priorityType":0,"stepAnime":false,"through":false,"trigger":3,"walkAnime":true}],"x":0,"y":0}
